    "name": "The South Island",
    "steam_appid": 3000020,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/8718e9bcdf36e9c879cfeff30f08e161.poster.avif?t=1764718022\" width=616 height=229 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/8718e9bcdf36e9c879cfeff30f08e161.webm?t=1764718022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>新挑战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一次绝望和勇气的举动后，Ayo发现自己与母亲分离，漂流在海洋中。在找到坚实的土地后，他遇到了一片新的挑战土地，一个充满神秘和危险的地方。在探索密林、开阔的田野和黑暗的洞穴时，面对各种敌人，从野生动物到敌对的土著战士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The South Island 是一款具有复古像素艺术风格的动作 RPG，灵感来自《塞尔达传说》（SNES）的探索玩法和《暗黑破坏神》（经典版）的进度系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/5b206a62ff66fe7336d84e29a05a8235.poster.avif?t=1764718022\" width=616 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/5b206a62ff66fe7336d84e29a05a8235.webm?t=1764718022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 一款专为类型爱好者制作的像素风格游戏，带来怀旧的体验；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索南方地图，欣赏美丽的动植物；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 帮助角色面对独特的敌人，随着进展收集物品和资源；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 使用本土武器进行战斗：斧头、矛、吹箭和弓箭；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 遇见首领，独特的实体，以及2D平台风格的战斗；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 迷你游戏、支线任务和引人入胜的故事。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/4165c2a88c112d3aa253d475f3e1fd95.apng?t=1764718022\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/4165c2a88c112d3aa253d475f3e1fd95.poster.avif?t=1764718022\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=229 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/4693a92a15328ff0b19cbd750d25ce85.apng?t=1764718022\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/4693a92a15328ff0b19cbd750d25ce85.poster.avif?t=1764718022\" class=\"bb_img\" width=615 height=126 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>勇敢的英雄</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助Ayo克服所有挑战，拯救他的母亲。面对强大的敌人，解决引人入胜的谜题，探索一个充满活力的世界。Ayo的勇气和决心将在每一步中受到考验。你准备好迎接这场史诗般的冒险了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/14fecb22327ab4e39e04bf4bb756701e.poster.avif?t=1764718022\" width=632 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/14fecb22327ab4e39e04bf4bb756701e.webm?t=1764718022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/14fecb22327ab4e39e04bf4bb756701e.mp4?t=1764718022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ÓGA地图</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到Ayo的避难所，这里是玩家休息、钓鱼、收集新资源、制作独特食物和手工艺品的圣地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/9c98e1837ab2c390102b36fc32037b9e.poster.avif?t=1764718022\" width=758 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/9c98e1837ab2c390102b36fc32037b9e.webm?t=1764718022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/9c98e1837ab2c390102b36fc32037b9e.mp4?t=1764718022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/d49c32c6cb88c069ea58f494809d9fe2.apng?t=1764718022\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000020/extras/d49c32c6cb88c069ea58f494809d9fe2.poster.avif?t=1764718022\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=229 /></picture></span></p>",
